<HEAD>Protest Forces Adjournment of City Council Meeting</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DALLAS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Chanting, flag-waving protesters forced an
adjournment of a City Council meeting, and a woman was knocked to
the floor when she was caught in a scuffle between security guards
and one of the protesters.
   Mayor Annette Strauss gaveled the meeting to an end after about
