doors from closing, but was pushed away by security guards who were
ushering the mayor out.
   Frances Penn, 76, was caught in the fracas and apparently was
knocked to the floor by Staples. Staples said he was pushed into
the woman by security guards.
   The woman was escorted out of City Hall by a paramedic, but she
declined medical treatment.
